Object.Field: RKM JDE Enterprise One SQL Server

COMPONENT NAME: RKM JDE Enterprise One SQL Server
AUTHOR: Oracle
DESCRIPTION: - Reverse engineering Knowledge Module to retrieve the tables and ztables for JDE Enterprise One. - This RKM is suitable for JDE installed on Microsoft SQL Server.
SQL Server database and schema that stores the JDE Central objects.
SQL Server database and schema that stores the JDE data dictionary. If database name is the same as the one set up in data server, it is optional.
SQL Server database and schema that stores JDE Object Librarian. If database name is the same as the one set up in data server, it is optional.
SQL Server database and schema that stores JDE Contral tables. If database name is the same as the one set up in data server, it is optional.
If this option is selected, data tables are reversed
If this option is selected, interface tables (ztables) are reversed.

DE System Short Name as (set % for all JDE System) : 00 Foundation Environment 01 Adress Book 02 Electronic Mail 03 Accounts Receivable etc ...
Or you can specify a list of modeles like '01','02','03'
Language used to recover the object description and comments. List of language : E English F French S Spanish
